languages.text: "Ткачам иногда приходится навещать этот отсек и забирать лишних, растрачивающих ресурс отсека".
languages.translation_comment: Pasqal: "Why is so much space allotted to the lower orders? It is inefficient. They could be accommodated much more compactly."

languages.text: "Spinners sometimes have to visit this bay and remove those who are a drain on its resources."
